This event aims to highlight the need for electoral reforms, and discuss what our legislators can pursue to improve the legal framework on Philippine elections in collaboration with various stakeholders.

A Colloquium on Electoral Reforms with the theme "Maximizing Opportunities and Valuing Elections through Electoral Reforms".
For the past six years, only a handful of electoral laws have been passed in Congress. In light of this trend, the Legal Network for Truthful Elections (LENTE) presents MOVE!
Electoral reforms also promote the rights of citizens, and increases the level of accountability, transparency, and inclusiveness of elections.
